    "Description": "Got a delivery request that could use you.\n~mission(Contractor|Family)\n\nPACKAGES FOR PICK UP (ANY ORDER)\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item1|SerialNumber)</EM4> from the <EM4>~mission(Pickup1|Address)</EM4>\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item2|SerialNumber)</EM4> from the <EM4>~mission(Pickup2|Address)</EM4>\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item3|SerialNumber)</EM4> from the <EM4>~mission(Pickup3|Address)</EM4>\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item4|SerialNumber)</EM4> from the <EM4>~mission(Pickup4|Address)</EM4>\n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item1|SerialNumber)</EM4> to the <EM4>~mission(Dropoff1|Address)</EM4>\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item2|SerialNumber)</EM4> to the <EM4>~mission(Dropoff2|Address)</EM4>\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item3|SerialNumber)</EM4> to the <EM4>~mission(Dropoff3|Address)</EM4>\n     \u00b7 Package <EM4>#~mission(Item4|SerialNumber)</EM4> to the <EM4>~mission(Dropoff4|Address)</EM4>\n\nLast thing, it'd probably be a good idea to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> with. \n\nThanks,\nConni Ling\nShipment Coordinator\nLing Family Hauling",
